title: Ebro In The Morning - Remembering Takeoff + Trying To Stay Positive
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 11/2/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about the tragic murder of Takeoff in Houston, Kyrie's ignorant comments, white-ish, and staying positive.

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
